name: vintage guitar pedal poster
description:
recently unearthed vintage guitar pedal poster by art director chris pieretti. poster is original dead stock from 2007. measures 33" x 22.5". comes neatly folded to 7.5" x 11". small quantity available 

features original, much sought after ibanez overdrive pro ts-808 tube screamer, boss chorus ensemble, roland phase II, fender phaser et al. 

very cool, offset printed, small run item fit for framing. printed on 60# offset opaque mohawk paper. 

email for special shipping to europe + asia.

name: spaceman sticker
description:
super large kubrick inspired mission 606 vinyl sticker by art director chris pieretti. printed on 6 mil vinyl with 3 mil clear coat. this sticker is heavy, thick + totally awesome. 

measures 5.75" x 8.75". recently featured in the db burkeman + monica locascio book 'stickers, stuck up piece of crap' 

very few left. great addition to your sticker colection.
